Two
police officers on Tuesday allegedly shot themselves dead in two separate
incidents in Mombasa County. In
the first incident, Dennis Kamau Ndungu, a General Service Unit (GSU) officer, is
said to have shot himself using his own pistol at his home in Nyali. Investigating
officers who visited the scene said they had recovered exhibits indicating that
Kamau had killed himself. "Glock19
Pistol with 12 rounds of ammunition, three spent cartridges and a shattered
Samsung mobile phone was recovered at the scene and kept as exhibits,"
