body of the deceased has since been moved to the Pandya hospital mortuary
awaiting postmortem. In
the second incident, an officer based at the Kiembeni Police Station in Kisauni
was also found by his colleagues having allegedly shot himself on Monday night. His
body was taken to Coast General Funeral Home. The
two incidences also follow another in Kiambu County where an officer attached to the presidential escort unit shot
himself dead inside the General Service Unit (GSU) camp in Juja.  A Jericho
pistol, 13 rounds of ammunition were recovered by officers who rushed to the
scene.